Introspection ​

Examples -> Introspection

The introspection extension adds an introspect method to conveniently introspect the schema.

Getting Started ​

This is a very simple extension, here's an example:

Introspection
ts
import { 
Introspection
 } from 'graffle/extensions/introspection'
import { 
Graffle
 } from './graffle/__.js'

const 
pokemon
 = 
Graffle
.
create
().
use
(
Introspection
())

const 
data
 = await 
pokemon
.
introspect
()
console.log(
data
)
